## Executive Summary

This roadmap defines the backend wiring strategy for VJLive3, orchestrating the integration of all systems across 8 phases. It establishes the data flow architecture, dependency matrix, and implementation sequence required to transform the modular codebase into a cohesive, production-ready system.

**Critical Objectives:**
- Ensure all plugins access required inputs (video, depth, audio, MIDI, OSC)
- Maintain 60 FPS sacred rail under all conditions
- Support hot-swapping of components without restart
- Enable agent orchestration and AI inference at scale
- Provide deployment-ready telemetry and monitoring

