## 6. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Context object becomes God object | High | Strict schema validation; split into sub-contexts if needed |
| Scheduler overhead > 2ms | High | Pre-compute schedule; cache batches; use Cython for hot path |
| Agent-Plugin bus introduces latency | Medium | Use lock-free dict; batch updates per frame |
| Telemetry overhead > 1ms | Medium | Sampling (1/4 frames); async aggregation |
| Config save/load version mismatch | Medium | Include schema version; migration scripts |
| Plugin crash recovery incomplete | High | Comprehensive error boundary tests; circuit breaker pattern |

